  },
  {
    "id": "NEG_003",
    "category": "name_equivalence",
    "scenario": "Corp. 与 Corporation 的等价差异（注意：Corp. 与 Company Limited 不等价，仍构成不符）",
    "lc_field": {
      "field": "beneficiary.name",
      "value": "Global Trade Corp."
    },
    "doc_field": {
      "document": "insurance_policy",
      "field": "insured",
      "value": "Global Trade Corporation"
    },
    "is_discrepancy": false,
    "explanation": "'Corp.' 是 'Corporation' 的标准缩写，属于公认的商业简称，不构成不符点。 重要提醒：Corp. 是 Corporation 的缩写，不是 Company Limited 的缩写。Corp. 与 Company Limited 之间的差异构成不符点。同理，Co., Ltd. 与 Company Limited 虽含义接近，但如果信用证写的是全称，单据使用缩写则构成不符。只有当缩写与其对应全称完全匹配时才不构成不符（如 Corp. = Corporation, Inc. = Incorporated）。"
  },
